@appHostUrl = http://localhost:5002
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!
@localeZh = zh-CN

### AppHost Root
GET {{appHostUrl}}/

### AppHost Health Live
GET {{appHostUrl}}/internal/health/live

### AppHost Health Ready
GET {{appHostUrl}}/internal/health/ready

### AppHost Health Live Report
GET {{appHostUrl}}/internal/health/live-report

### AppHost Health Ready Report
GET {{appHostUrl}}/internal/health/ready-report

### AppHost Login (via AppAuthController)
# @name appLogin
POST {{appHostUrl}}/auth/app/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Accept-Language: {{localeZh}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@appToken = {{appLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### AppHost - Me
GET {{appHostUrl}}/auth/app/me
Authorization: Bearer {{appToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### AppHost - Logout
POST {{appHostUrl}}/auth/app/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{appToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### AppHost Login (API v1 compatibility)
# @name appLoginCompat
POST {{appHostUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Accept-Language: {{localeZh}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@appTokenCompat = {{appLoginCompat.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}
@refreshTokenCompat = {{appLoginCompat.response.body.$.data.refreshToken}}

### AppHost Refresh (API v1 compatibility)
POST {{appHostUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshTokenCompat}}"
}

### AppHost Me (API v1 compatibility)
GET {{appHostUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{appTokenCompat}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### AppHost Logout (API v1 compatibility)
POST {{appHostUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{appTokenCompat}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### AppHost Swagger
GET {{appHostUrl}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
